            <div class="data-card-head" style="background: #e0f2fe;">
                <h6><i class="bi bi-house-door"></i> Depodaki Malzeme Stokları <span class="record-count">@(((List<AritmaEnvanter.Models.Entities.DepoStok>)ViewBag.DepoStoklar).Count) farklı malzeme</span></h6>
            </div>
            <div style="overflow-x:auto;">
